OL,3,CFinancial worries put medieval
OL,4,CCumbrian fair at risk
OL,6,FUncertainty is surrounding the future
OL,7,Fof a long-standing fair in West
OL,8,FCumbria.
OL,10,FEgremont's Crab Fair dates back to
OL,11,F1267, making it one of the oldest in
OL,12,Fthe world.
OL,14,FDuring the annual event in September
OL,15,Fpeople gather to see ancient
OL,16,Ftraditions such as the World Gurning
OL,17,FChampionships and the apple cart
OL,18,Fparade.
