OL,3,CFinancial worries put medieval
OL,4,CCumbrian fair at risk
OL,6,FIt also involves more modern
OL,7,Fattractions, such as fair ground
OL,8,Frides, children's entertainment and
OL,9,Flive music.
OL,11,FHowever, the future of the fair is now
OL,12,Funder threat and organisers are
OL,13,Fappealing for help after this year's
OL,14,Fevent resulted in a #17,000 loss.
OL,16,FThe volunteers who run it say before
OL,17,Fthe Covid-19 pandemic the event was
OL,18,Fbecoming more self-sufficient, with
OL,19,Ffunds raised from the year before
OL,20,Fcovering the majority of the costs for
OL,21,Fthe following year.
