OL,3,CFinancial worries put medieval
OL,4,CCumbrian fair at risk
OL,6,FThen, in September this year, Crab
OL,7,FFair weekend was hit with heavy rain
OL,8,Fand poor weather conditions, meaning
OL,9,Fpoor turn out and once again little
OL,10,Fmoney made.
OL,12,FPlanning has already started for 2026,
OL,13,Fbut the volunteer organisers are now
OL,14,Fappealing for more financial support
OL,15,Ffrom the local community.
OL,17,FApart from during the World Wars, the
OL,18,Ffair has only been cancelled three
OL,19,Ftimes - Twice during the pandemic and
OL,20,Fonce following the death of the Queen.
